.TH "nvme_get_features_simple" 9 "nvme_get_features_simple" "July 2025" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_get_features_simple \- Helper function for @nvme_get_features()
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" nvme_get_features_simple
.BI "(int fd "  ","
.BI "enum nvme_features_id fid "  ","
.BI "__u32 nsid "  ","
.BI "__u32 *result "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "fd" 12
File descriptor of nvme device
.IP "fid" 12
Feature identifier
.IP "nsid" 12
Namespace ID, if applicable
.IP "result" 12
The command completion result from CQE dword0
.SH "RETURN"
The nvme command status if a response was received (see
\fIenum nvme_status_field\fP) or -1 with errno set otherwise.
